dataSet.name: DataSet1
dataSet.query:
SELECT ALLOWED SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.Incomings) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverCr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9001, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.CostOfGoodsSold) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9002, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.Expenses) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9007, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.OtherIncome) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverCr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9101, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.OtherExpenses) OR AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.CreditInterestRates) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9102, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.ProfitLosses) AND AdministrativeTurnovers.BalancedAccount.TypeOfAccount <> VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.UndistributedProfit) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverCr - AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9901, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.ProfitTax) AND AdministrativeTurnovers.BalancedAccount.TypeOfAccount <> VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.UndistributedProfit) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr - AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverCr ELSE 0 END) AS Account9902, SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.ProfitLosses) AND AdministrativeTurnovers.BalancedAccount.TypeOfAccount <> VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.UndistributedProfit) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverCr - AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN AdministrativeTurnovers.Account.TypeOfAccount = VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.ProfitTax) AND AdministrativeTurnovers.BalancedAccount.TypeOfAccount <> VALUE(Enum.GLAccountsTypes.UndistributedProfit) THEN AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverDr - AdministrativeTurnovers.AmountTurnoverCr ELSE 0 END) AS Account99, AdministrativeTurnovers.Company FROM AccountingRegister.Managerial.Turnovers(, , , , PlanningPeriod = VALUE(Catalog.PlanningPeriods.Actual), ) AS AdministrativeTurnovers
GROUP BY AdministrativeTurnovers.Company
